                              automata.scm

Implementation of both Deterministic Finite Automata (DFAs) and
Nondeterministic Finite Automata (NFAs) on r7rs scheme, using
SRFI 1 and SRFI 113.

The file ./automata.scm contains the implementation of the procedures
to make a DFA (make-dfa), make a NFA (make-nfa) and run either one on
a string (automaton-run).

The file ./exempla.scm contains examples of DFAs and NFAs implemented
using the procedures of the other file.   This is an executable file;
when run, it computes those automata on a set of predefined strings.

Public domain.
